title: This Beautiful Brunette Has Become A Fly Fishing Sensation [SLIDESHOW]
text:
5495092 Maddie Brenneman has become a fly fishing sensation and it’s certainly not hard to see why. Not only is the Colorado native a sight for sore eyes, but she also happens to be an incredible fly fisher and (presumably) a pretty good fly fishing guide, too.
A post shared by Maddie Brenneman (@maddiebrenneman) on Feb 7, 2016 at 9:45am PST 

The beautiful brunette has over 88,000 followers on Instagram where she shares pictures of some impressive trout and the breathtaking locations that her job takes her to. Here are 14 of Maddie’s most amazing photos.
